channel.title: [Brazil][German] Rsbot 230 - brazilian server][Leaked/100% safe]
channel.description:
To run it in Brazil/German worlds, please follow the directions: 1) Download: 2) Extract to desktop 3) Open the folder, click "GermanBeta", then the Rsbot Jar. 4) Once you login a GUI will pop up. Make sure it's not on Less CPU, or it might freeze up. 5)The gui will ask which World to load(Brazil/German) And will load all the scripts, for specified language. 6)If for some reason a script is not there, or I just coverted a new one, scroll down on this thread, and I have it uploaded on pastebin, :) 7)The bot does do randoms, so to prevent log out, you can save your info in the Account interface, but this 100% optional. [COLOR="Red"][SIZE="5"]This bot is still in Beta Stages, please report any bugs.[/SIZE][/COLOR] [img]http://img823.imageshack.us/img823/8767/mediaa.th.png[/img] Here are some scripts, which I have already completed, :) [Code]aKillaBrazil.java http://pastebin.com/9cvtvU5Z AangRootsBrasil.java http://pastebin.com/m7CxwAjN VEChopperBrazil.java http://pastebin.com/T30L5khs (thanks to MossyCoffee) TFighterBrazil.java: http://pastebin.com/jLBRuegL (thanks to exotikfor fixing my mistake) YakKillerBrazil.java http://pastebin.com/dNqdnK37 BarbarianAgilityBrazil.java http://pastebin.com/2GiZKwLV (performs REGULAR Barbarian course flawlessly)(thanks to exotik) mPlankerBrazil.java http://pastebin.com/ktPX5sWh (balloon option does not work dont use it, -1 to never rest)[/code]
Bankpins = Done (in theory none of my accounts had a bank pin ) Beehive solver = Done Closeallinterface = Done (nothing changed) Lost and found = Done Login Bot = 90% (havent got the "runescape updated", "login server down" and "to many connections" first 2 don't really matter as they wont get you banned, last one who knows.) Improved rewards box = Done Quiz solver = Done Freaky forester = Done Mime = Done . Capn Arnav = Done (in theory but meh) Pinball = Done Drill Demon = Done Certer = Done Molly/Evil twin = Done Scaperune island = Done (missed her saying "Wait! Before" will see if that affects da bot. Frog cave = need Pillory (jail cell getting tomatoes chucked at you) *member(?)* = need Gravedigger = need Exam (dragon school teacher/mr mordaut) 3/30 questions + 1/4 doors (for sure) Prison (balloon popping one) = need Sandwich lady = need
Also, We have converted the Loading to german. Only a few german scripts, at the moment. Videos: [url=http://img109.imageshack.us/i/ky6.mp4/]http://img109.imageshack.us/i/ky6.mp4/[/url] ----> Language Switch [url=http://img15.imageshack.us/i/a4i.mp4/]http://img15.imageshack.us/i/a4i.mp4/[/url] ----> Chickens now German! [url=http://img820.imageshack.us/i/uvu.mp4/]http://img820.imageshack.us/i/uvu.mp4/[/url] ----> Akilla now German! [url=http://img22.imageshack.us/i/642.mp4/]http://img22.imageshack.us/i/642.mp4/[/url] ----> Evil Twin Random [3/21/11]. [img]http://img641.imageshack.us/img641/1580/18943026.png[/img]
